Class SceneView

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • javax.swing.JComponent
          • javax.swing.JPanel
            • cisc275.group3.view.SceneView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class SceneView
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    Takes in an underlying JPanel and overlays the user interface via JLayeredPanes. There are different constructors that accommodate different layer requirements.
